T1  - MechAgents: Large language model multi-agent collaborations can solve mechanics problems, generate new data, and integrate knowledge
AU  - Ni, Bo
AU  - Buehler, Markus J.
JO  - Extreme Mechanics Letters
VL  - 67
SP  - 102131
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2024/03/01/
SN  - 2352-4316
